reviewText: Fun concept with lots of scope for create output. Also great documentation, although the game/toy itself is fairly straight forward to figure out. It would be nice if you could scroll and zoom around a little faster, but this doesn't affect the enjoyment of playing with the software. Would recommend to anyone with a musical streak.
